## Living documentation

The project keeps an always-current, token-cheap snapshot of its own state so agents get context
without re-scanning everything.

- `docs/ai/PROJECT-STATE.md` — overview, module map, lightweight decisions log, current status.
- `docs/ai/ARCHITECTURE.md` — architecture with **Mermaid** diagrams.

**Keep it fresh:** run `/doc-sync` (Claude) or the `doc-sync` prompt (Copilot) when you finish a task.
<% if (it.sdd.backend !== "none") { %>It derives change status from `openspec/changes/*`.<% } %> Read these files first; they are cheaper than scanning the repo.
